These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, lavender
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, crime
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, august
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Color         | lavender | lilac  |
| Movie-Genre       | crime    | zombie    |
| Birthday   | august       | may      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, lily
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, skateboard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
City: miami, san-francisco
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Flower      | lily     | iris |
| Transport           | bus | skateboard      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| City         | miami | san-francisco     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
