1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who likes purple is the dressmaker##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Color      | purple | aquamarine  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | satire   |
| Job     | dressmaker     | bartender |

