.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, mauve
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, australian
1. the argentine is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Color          | mauve         | azure    |
| Transport           | taxi | roller    |
| Nationality   | argentine           | australian   |

