.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, lime
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, snowboarding
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker
1. the coach is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Food   | broccoli          | lime |
| Sport           | ice-hockey          | snowboarding    |
| Game     | snooker            | mah-jongg       |

 